entries.journal_entry_description: The Alliance is stepping-up the war effort in Restuss and needs more weapons. Lieutenant Ingri has asked you to make a rocket launcher for the cause.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You have been tasked with creating a rocket launcher for the Rebel Alliance.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have completed the rocket launcher for the troops in Restuss and should return to Lieutenant Ingri with them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Give the rocket launcher to the load lifter droid.
